   Trimac to Buy Transit Business
</HL>
<DATE>
07/31/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B12
</SO>
<CO>
   T.TMA CP T.CP
</CO>
<LP>
   CALGARY, Alberta -- Trimac Ltd. said its Trimac
Transportation System subsidiary agreed to acquire CP Bulk
Systems, a unit of Canadian Pacific Ltd. Terms weren't
disclosed.
   Trimac said CP Bulk is a transportation concern
specializing in bulk commodities and generated revenue last
year of about 40 million Canadian dollars (US$34.7 million).
The proposed transaction is subject to regulatory approval.
</LP>
