</SO>
<LP>
   Vintage Wisdom
                                                                                                       

</LP>
<TEXT>
   White wine with fish,
   Red with meat.
   With the main course, dry;
   With dessert, it's sweet.
   But there's one wine for sure
   That's bound to no norm,
   Since, as everyone knows,
   It's any port in a storm.
   -- Peter Friedman.
   ---
   Sad Cycle
                                                                                                       

   Not only do parents start out with another mouth to feed,
they end up with another mouth they have to listen to.
   -- John Drybred.
   ---
   Daffynition
                                                                                                       

   Mount Ararat: point of Noah return.
   -- Jon Allen.
