<LP>
   JOHANNESBURG, South Africa -- Rustenburg Platinum Holdings
Ltd. said its earnings fell 7.5% in the year ended June 30.
   Net profit amounted to 551.3 million rand ($211.3 million)
from the previous financial year's figure of 595.7 million
rand. Earnings amounted to 440.0 cents ($1.68) a share
compared with 475.4 cents the previous year.
